{"tid":2068170,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港大法律學院洩逾2,500學生私隱 受害人憂資料經內地生「送中」","createTime":"2020-06-17T13:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:14:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eb14c22dcc124749afe4069cd3415ac2023aaeb8","tid":2068170,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200617/7JXNEOFKLV7AO2KNDBETUUKUGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2F7JXNEOFKLV7AO2KNDBETUUKUGE%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=94770277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2F7JXNEOFKLV7AO2KNDBETUUKUGE%2F&h=965380bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200617/7JXNEOFKLV7AO2KNDBETUUKUGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院爆出洩露學生個人資料風波。學院今午以電郵通知全院學生，指院方日前誤將一份載有全院逾2,500名學生個人資料的文件，寄至其中71名學生的電郵中。院方就事件向學生致歉，並指已成功要求其中64人刪除文件。惟受害學生要求校方就事件作出調查並以報告交代。"},{"pid":"a7c63a19c227be768b4d7a857f3afa5dff686f5a","tid":2068170,"uid":249885,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"hku shenzhen"},{"pid":"23247434c49a5e16590b2e7e4b05b0c7ea2cfa52","tid":2068170,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7c63a19c227be768b4d7a857f3afa5dff686f5a","tid":2068170,"uid":249885,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"hku shenzhen"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443c51f90ee6bb723b9e8f36cd81692336fbde34","tid":2068170,"uid":37596,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"扮洩露<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg